Posts.EditableText:
So apparently doing this doesn't work

```
      player.changedStatus => {
        JS.eval ("$('#status-span').html('" + player.Status + "%"');")
      }
```

But this does:

```
      player.changedStatus => {
        JS.eval ("$('#status-span').html('" + player.Status + "%" + "');")
      }
```

So it appears to be problem solved.
